Initial Project Setup:

Create a new React project with TypeScript:

bash
npx create-react-app dynamic-form-generator --template typescript

Install dependencies:
bash
npm install tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer react-hook-form react-json-view @types/react-json-view
npm install jest @testing-library/react @testing-library/jest-dom --save-dev
npm install playwright --save-dev

Initialize Tailwind CSS:
bash

npx tailwindcss init
Configure tailwind.config.js with a basic setup.

Add Tailwind CSS to index.css:
css

@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;
